      "    * The longer wavelengths – red and orange – are able to pass through the atmosphere more directly, giving us those beautiful sunset colors.\n",
      "\n",
      "\n",
      "\n",
      "**In short:** The sky is blue because air molecules scatter blue light from the sun more than they scatter other colors.\n",
